  </p>

  <p>
    Shea BJ, Reeves BC, Wells G, et al. AMSTAR 2: a critical appraisal tool for systematic reviews.
    <em>BMJ</em> 2017;358:j4008.
  </p>

  <p>
    Whiting PF, Rutjes AW, Westwood ME, et al. QUADAS-2: a revised tool for the quality assessment of
